name: PathCapType
description: The shape to be drawn at the ends of a path

content.name: None
content.description: No shape is drawn. The ends of the path will be flat.

content.name: Square
content.description: Half a square is drawn on the end of the path's ends

content.name: Round
content.description: Half a circle is drawn on the end of the path's ends, with a number of points defined by the provided value
